{"tid":1780451,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"最近想領養貓，但俾啲貓義工玩到傻","createTime":"2019-12-12T11:11:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T21:42:11.000Z","uid":19166,"like":35,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"7df1c91ddc078141060c7163eb46ebd26a504d40","tid":1780451,"uid":19166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T11:11:49.000Z","msg":"有一個我上埋去睇貓，又話見我有養緊貓所以俾我，而唔俾另一個人，仲約實埋幾時接貓返屋企。最後即晚話隻貓俾左第二個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有個仲on9，問左我成2個星期問題。佢有好多隻貓俾我睇，最後又話送曬俾人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw，有冇巴絲有好貓義工推介？本身有養緊貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\ntg: @justinchanfake"},{"pid":"ee375353da8b88cd7e3535711b93c20b8b1f9af2","tid":1780451,"uid":229436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T11:19:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hkscda.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkscda.com%2F&d=Vh0AUGqI%2BhuKY3uG7C8Fc3O0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=380ecbe5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkscda.com/</a><br />\n香港拯救貓狗協會 (簡稱HKSCDA) 是一個於2007年4月1日正式成立的本地非牟利組織。本會一直致力為流浪貓狗提供糧食、醫療、絕育及領養等服務。除了拯救繁殖場的毛孩，主動援救流浪街頭的受傷貓狗外，本會亦會接收被市民遺棄的小動物，並盡力為牠們尋覓可信的主人覓尋一個永遠的家。<br />\n<br />\n佢地有搞定期領養活動。另外都可以上去睇 不過佢地都好忙 唔會即時應到機"},{"pid":"d25e5c19541a4c135e8a5b07508b57e509cda602","tid":1780451,"uid":60655,"like":67,"dislike":25,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T11:21:41.000Z","msg":"直接買隻，個d所謂既貓義工<br />\n<br />\n10個有8個，唔係扮上菜就根本唔想俾你<br />\n<br />\n最好你課埋金俾佢養貓"},{"pid":"1ed3bc99754fb9aa783632d3e0c521ac3b59373b","tid":1780451,"uid":54930,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T11:24:31.000Z","msg":"月經post"},{"pid":"7873b4dafe7f9e08207d51c557a3c42829d422c7","tid":1780451,"uid":202889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite