\n除時俾隻花貓你就想r 你課幾皮"},{"pid":"a63eb77289684ae1b7bffbc1e59fef08ca61cbfc","tid":1780451,"uid":50513,"like":3,"dislike":19,"score":-16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T12:06:16.000Z","msg":"盡量唔好買<br />\n街貓好多都病貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去愛協果d領養啦<br />\n<br />\n果d會打晒針<br />\n又可以用佢地d service（絕育之類）<br />\n<br />\n利申 屋企兩隻都係愛協拎返黎"},{"pid":"d72292b2f32922db0a3bf872b8b1f5f8b4673d93","tid":1780451,"uid":50513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a63eb77289684ae1b7bffbc1e59fef08ca61cbfc","tid":1780451,"uid":50513,"like":3,"dislike":19,"score":-16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T12:06:16.000Z","msg":"盡量唔好買<br />\n街貓好多都病貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去愛協果d領養啦<br />\n<br />\n果d會打晒針<br />\n又可以用佢地d service（絕育之類）<br />\n<br />\n利申 屋企兩隻都係愛協拎返黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T12:06:46.000Z","msg":"街*買*好多都病貓"},{"pid":"7366a93368fa2d98c609ca97c6db5ad83d946817","tid":1780451,"uid":178066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7df1c91ddc078141060c7163eb46ebd26a504d40","tid":1780451,"uid":19166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T11:11:49.000Z","msg":"有一個我上埋去睇貓，又話見我有養緊貓所以俾我，而唔俾另一個人，仲約實埋幾時接貓返屋企。最後即晚話隻貓俾左第二個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有個仲on9，問左我成2個星期問題。佢有好多隻貓俾我睇，最後又話送曬俾人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw，有冇巴絲有好貓義工推介？本身有養緊貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\ntg: @justinchanfake"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T12:13:38.000Z","msg":"試下貓朋狗友行動派<br />\n之前領養問過佢地，好好禮貌"},{"pid":"c60a89d7d46093b4d44cb7c4d1787ae29011375b","tid":1780451,"uid":178800,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"f1dc02976520cd11fa9ca927e45db6b7b75e3d28","tid":1780451,"uid":180404,"like":42,"dislike":11,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T11:35:39.000Z","msg":"直接買過隻好過<br />\n我都有類似經驗<br />\n<br />\n一開始打算好心領養，幫下d貓貓，唔幫襯d店<br />\n結果換黎就係比人百般刁難<br />\n我唔想講收入，就唔比我領養<br />\n我心諗，唔講咪唔講囉，我做左咁多年專業人士，人工分分鐘鐘你全家加埋都唔夠我高...但我又一定要話比你個外人知?<br />\n<br />\n最後買過隻算. 無謂受氣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T12:18:44.000Z","msg":"真，雖然領養係好事<br />\n但個過程好反智<br />\n不了"},{"pid":"f92222627736e9bfad8b4ae652d8440aaad883d4","tid":1780451,"uid":19166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T15:20:50.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e77fa3cf052472e8f1b4aac70d45d2cafbe7dea8","tid":1780451,"uid":149829,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T15:44:22.000Z","msg":"有個上我屋企左睇右睇, 最後兩隻想養既都俾左另一個人, 之後又話仲有一隻可以, 但最後又係俾左人, 原因係果啲人有養開貓, 咁係咪鼓勵我地呢啲新手買貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搵左咁耐領養, 仲因為咁特登去裝窗網, 最後都係得個吉<br />\n其實好聽就係領養, 事實係大家都想搵一隻唔駛錢又靚既貓<br />\n有好多老病顏色唔靚既, 都冇人領養<br />\n真正既領養係領養呢啲貓<br />\n不過揀隻自己鐘意既係人之常情,但領養到一隻心儀既, 就唔好站在道德高地話人地買貓, 咁樣真係好嘔心<br />\n實情領養一隻靚+性格好+&lt;6個月既貓難度係極高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申已經試左10幾隻, 諗住去買貓"},{"pid":"fff8c0a2b0c7a53219390c79114068702d4ebbb6","tid":1780451,"uid":71657,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T15:46:32.000Z","msg":"大家買貓邊間買？<br />\n唔想幫襯黑店買病貓"},{"pid":"3da3ae1b3fa03da872426924f54eb9fa0c2f527d","tid":1780451,"uid":149829,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T15:46:50.000Z","msg":"回樓主<br />\n我相信靚既貓通常都係會俾義工自己收編, 或者俾左熟人"},{"pid":"c587edba6f92d7faa7282638b7bc8a9a7b59fed5","tid":1780451,"uid":19166,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e77fa3cf052472e8f1b4aac70d45d2cafbe7dea8","tid":1780451,"uid":149829,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T15:44:22.000Z","msg":"有個上我屋企左睇右睇, 最後兩隻想養既都俾左另一個人, 之後又話仲有一隻可以, 但最後又係俾左人, 原因係果啲人有養開貓, 咁係咪鼓勵我地呢啲新手買貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搵左咁耐領養, 仲因為咁特登去裝窗網, 最後都係得個吉<br />\n其實好聽就係領養, 事實係大家都想搵一隻唔駛錢又靚既貓<br />\n有好多老病顏色唔靚既, 都冇人領養<br />\n真正既領養係領養呢啲貓<br />\n不過揀隻自己鐘意既係人之常情,但領養到一隻心儀既, 就唔好站在道德高地話人地買貓, 咁樣真係好嘔心<br />\n實情領養一隻靚+性格好+&lt;6個月既貓難度係極高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申已經試左10幾隻, 諗住去買貓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T15:49:05.000Z","msg":"去到最後直路之後同你講<br />\nsorry，隻貓俾左第二個人<br />\n真係好撚sad，好撚無奈<br />\n已經冇乜動力再揾領養"},{"pid":"61fc0748ff19ca916b4a7d0bdb2bd4d5d7c840cb","tid":1780451,"uid":76744,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T16:06:28.000Z","msg":"四個月大接佢地番黎 宜家都就歲半喇<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QBy8iKU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQBy8iKU.png&h=084fec33&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"50c17a87fa8636a7fd7deb8d88aa287b36f6a1a1","tid":1780451,"uid":46050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T16:08:42.000Z","msg":"睇下小豆丁啦 有一胎準備出領養"},{"pid":"3cfb6e0b8671c05cc24784c36b46a1388e7d8cdd","tid":1780451,"uid":76744,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T16:10:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bGyPNEz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbGyPNEz.jpg&h=1048f2ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可以去睇下 完全唔同出面d痴線貓義工"},{"pid":"99ddf19e121c76214ac8637170793dde65b55ed5","tid":1780451,"uid":305735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T16:24:15.000Z","msg":"申請時有埋窗網會快好多，因為同一隻貓會有好幾個人想要，兩個禮拜太耐喇"},{"pid":"1867841671fa7fc32e69c034bec0d551f17e0385","tid":1780451,"uid":19166,"like":0,"dislike":0,