dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d6280fa7dfd0d647b5dae8e2de382b580733a17","tid":1780451,"uid":326825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"985cfee303ae1018a95a395263121b14caed954c","tid":1780451,"uid":254703,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T08:51:11.000Z","msg":"去愛協領養，好快手，裡面好多貓貓等緊你，盡量真係唔好幫襯賣貓個D，太唔道德啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我之前都係討論區上面領養過一隻普通家貓，埋單$500，冇家訪，仲同我去寵物店買貓用既用品，以家養到肥肥白白，所以唔好因為一時之氣而幫襯無良商人，d貓好慘架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T08:54:39.000Z","msg":"推 <br />\n<br />\n好多貓仲係唔同協會等緊人領養<br />\n唔跟義工領養都有其他選擇"},{"pid":"4a77c4ea6025929058cec0f0e665409ef73fcf9d","tid":1780451,"uid":94665,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T08:57:09.000Z","msg":"其實可能係我好彩<br />\n三次都係係同一個貓義工到領養<br />\n佢一毫子都無收過我仲借左個籠俾我用成年<br />\n第一次係等左兩個星期<br />\n因為整窗網<br />\n之後都係即日睇貓即日拎貓<br />\n所以我少少懷疑連登屌柒貓異工班人其實係唔係開寵物店驚無生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfcdca9182ebc88fde41e53c711c1adf37a4de1f","tid":1780451,"uid":64787,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T10:25:45.000Z","msg":"之前想養狗，本身諗住領養<br />\n跟住上網見到有個領養狗狗post, 見到合眼緣就whatsapp個義工<br />\n我問係咪有狗狗領養<br />\n佢問左幾條我背景問題<br />\n我答完佢<br />\n佢就話好的等等，我睇睇隻狗俾人領養左未先<br />\n<br />\n我心諗，我連邊隻狗都未提...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 除非佢真係得一隻啦"},{"pid":"b5ee62e6ce560c222659b66b66c997092c54f3af","tid":1780451,"uid":259973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7df1c91ddc078141060c7163eb46ebd26a504d40","tid":1780451,"uid":19166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T11:11:49.000Z","msg":"有一個我上埋去睇貓，又話見我有養緊貓所以俾我，而唔俾另一個人，仲約實埋幾時接貓返屋企。最後即晚話隻貓俾左第二個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有個仲on9，問左我成2個星期問題。佢有好多隻貓俾我睇，最後又話送曬俾人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw，有冇巴絲有好貓義工推介？本身有養緊貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\ntg: @justinchanfake"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T10:30:01.000Z","msg":"連登有個貓領養群，最近整嘅"},{"pid":"ef1af8100632a1a1f389752ead297f287e2d54fc","tid":1780451,"uid":264313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T16:42:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80fe871b8ac5eb0d9dc23f4a99916af66d9f15b0","tid":1780451,"uid":140742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T18:54:09.000Z","msg":"想養多隻 有冇唔西義工？pm唔該"},{"pid":"af159d98870fae135af581f9dff02990c14f2d2c","tid":1780451,"uid":777,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T23:44:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://t.me/lindonpet\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Flindonpet&d=Vh0AUGqI%2BhuKY3uG7C8Fc3O0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=a6220a9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/lindonpet</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我哋係連寵<br />\n我哋係一班喺連登發起嘅愛動物巴絲<br />\n好希望可以帶到新風氣俾大家<br />\n因為領養真係一件非常好嘅事<br />\n<br />\n如果你填左會waiting list<br />\n我哋出貓嗰陣就會match<br />\nmatch左了解過係啱先會做其他家居上嘅野<br />\n會先邀請你嚟探貓貓<br />\n同你傾吓計<br />\n因為我哋覺得事在人為<br />\n領養人嘅品格同態度比一切更重要<br />\n而且個個都做家訪嘅話其實我哋都唔得閒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外如果你填左好耐都冇人搵你<br />\n無論係義工表定係領養表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好意思因為我哋人手真係好短缺<br />\n建議你入gp一齊傾下討論下<br />\n同埋的而且確令人方面我哋係會開放比貓舍義工先<br />\n因為佢哋真係日日對住佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出心出力咁照顧比佢哋我覺得都合理<br />\n咁當然都係會做晒所有一般嘅程序<br />\n唔係係義工就9俾<br />\n<br />\n另外我哋其實好歡迎新手貓奴想來學習下點樣湊貓<br />\n一方面又可以同你地傾多啲計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87b9d825cc1236d32a345822698383e3289832c2","tid":1780451,"uid":777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af159d98870fae135af581f9dff02990c14f2d2c","tid":1780451,"uid":777,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T23:44:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://t.me/lindonpet\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Flindonpet&d=Vh0AUGqI%2BhuKY3uG7C8Fc3O0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=a6220a9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/lindonpet</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我哋係連寵<br />\n我哋係一班喺連登發起嘅愛動物巴絲<br />\n好希望可以帶到新風氣俾大家<br />\n因為領養真係一件非常好嘅事<br />\n<br />\n如果你填左會waiting list<br />\n我哋出貓嗰陣就會match<br />\nmatch左了解過係啱先會做其他家居上嘅野<br />\n會先邀請你嚟探貓貓<br />\n同你傾吓計<br />\n因為我哋覺得事在人為<br />\n領養人嘅品格同態度比一切更重要<br />\n而且個個都做家訪嘅話其實我哋都唔得閒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外如果你填左好耐都冇人搵你<br />\n無論係義工表定係領養表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好意思因為我哋人手真係好短缺<br />\n建議你入gp一齊傾下討論下<br />\n同埋的而且確令人方面我哋係會開放比貓舍義工先<br />\n因為佢哋真係日日對住佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出心出力咁照顧比佢哋我覺得都合理<br />\n咁當然都係會做晒所有一般嘅程序<br />\n唔係係義工就9俾<br />\n<br />\n另外我哋其實好歡迎新手貓奴想來學習下點樣湊貓<br />\n一方面又可以同你地傾多啲計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T23:45:40.000Z","msg":"同埋的而且確<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">領養</span></strong>*"},{"pid":"50343789adc070a103982f51bfe3b3f2e1b7219e","tid":1780451,"uid":193131,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T23:49:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔通我真係咁好彩<br />\n果時搵貓義工領養，係領